(1, 'admin', '$2y$10$5YOQi5cLhORxyqMr8kVPJeZuAdh9SxMBqYZ3prbNu2a2zJkZvn8La', 'Arianne Danielle', 'V.', 'Añora', 'ariannedanielleanora@gmail.com', 'https://github.com/ariabytes', 'www.linkedin.com/in/ariannedanielleañora', 'Hi, I\'m Arianne! I\'m a 2nd Year Bachelor of Science in Information Technology student at the University of Mindanao. I have a genuine passion for IT — what excites me most is how wide its scope is, from breadboarding circuits and crimping ethernet cables, to designing interfaces in Figma and building responsive layouts with Bootstrap and CSS. I enjoy both the technical and creative sides of the field, and I especially love the logic and problem-solving aspect of coding — there\'s something satisfying about making things work the way they should. I\'m a consistent honor student who takes pride in my work, and I love that IT is a field where there\'s always something new to learn and experience!', , '2026-03-16 00:29:27');

